## Quality Checklist

### Marketing Copy Review Checklist
- [ ] Content clearly positions within FastLane/SideLane/SlowLane framework
- [ ] Language is authoritative and stoic
- [ ] Messaging targets ambitious men 18-35
- [ ] Content avoids therapy/self-help language
- [ ] Calls-to-action are clear and compelling
- [ ] Value propositions are specific and measurable
- [ ] Social proof is included where relevant
- [ ] Content aligns with Trajectory brand values
- [ ] Copy is free of generic motivational language
- [ ] All claims are backed by experience or data
